      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "Experimental validation — hemolysis index comparison against FDA benchmark data",
      "description": "CFD-predicted normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) compared against published FDA benchmark experimental measurements for the generic centrifugal pump at 2500 RPM, 3500 RPM, and 4500 RPM across flow rates of 2.5 and 5.0 L/min. Mean absolute relative error of 8.3% across all operating points. Relative hemolysis index RH < 1 for all worst-case configurations tested. Validation activity conducted on the same geometry and boundary conditions as the COU.",
